reviews.text: A bakery situated in the lower level of Tampines One offers a wide selection of breads and cakes at reasonable prices.  Checkout service is efficient, though the store layout could be improved.  Overall, it is recommended.

Yamazaki at Tampines 1 offers mouthwatering baked bread that's freshly baked to perfection - soft, fluffy, and utterly delicious!

Was queuing up carrying my baby with me holding onto a tray of bread and this senior lady (couldnt get her name) came forward and assist me to let me make payment first. This kind gesture of her really makes my day and company should appreciate employees like her. Thank you. :)

My favourite Japanese flour bread n cake shop. Good selection of soft bread n crispy donuts, sandwiches n Japanese light cream cakes. They make good lunch meal if one like to eat light n finish with a nice sweet desert. There is always something yummy to wet your appetite. Try it for a change, you will come back for more. The colourful shelf display will make one happy.
